Scotland":"英国苏格兰艾斯爾","lifeSummary":"当Sir David Muir of Polkelly于1174年出生在英国苏格兰艾斯爾时，他的父亲Reginald Muir of Polkelly, King of the Northern Isles and Argyll \"having descended from the O'Moores of Ireland. The Muirs of Polkelly may have been the senior Muir line.\"25岁，母亲Fonia Moray29岁。他于大约1200年与Lady Isabel Graham在英国苏格兰艾斯爾结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和2个女儿的父母。他去世于1249年在他的家乡享年75岁，埋葬在苏格兰艾斯爾。"},"hr":{"1174–1249":"1174.–1249.","1176–1296":"1176–1296","1200–1280":"1200.–1280","1233–1285":"1233.–1285","1234–1295":"1234–1295","1149–1199":"1149–1199.","1145–1200":"1145–1200.","1176":"1176","1285":"1285","1296":"1296","1174":"1174.","1295":"1295","1280":"1280","1249":"1249.","1149":"1149","1234":"1234","1200":"1200.","1233":"1233.","1145":"1145","1199":"1199.","about 1200":"oko 1200.","about 1234":"oko 1234.","Polkelly, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Ayrshire, Škotska, United Kingdom","Kintyre, Argyll, Scotland":"Kintyre, Argyll, Scotland","Craig, Angus, Scotland":"Craig, Angus, Škotska, United Kingdom","Ayr, South Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Škotska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1174–1249":"1174–1249","1176–1296":"1176–1296","1200–1280":"1200–1280","1233–1285":"1233–1285","1234–1295":"1234–1295","1149–1199":"1149–1199","1145–1200":"1145–1200","1176":"1176","1285":"1285","1296":"1296","1174":"1174","1295":"1295","1280":"1280","1249":"1249","1149":"1149","1234":"1234","1200":"1200","1233":"1233","1145":"1145","1199":"1199","about 1200":"okolo 1200","about 1234":"okolo 1234","Polkelly, Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Ayrshire, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Kintyre, Argyll, Scotland":"Kintyre, Argyll, Scotland","Craig, Angus, Scotland":"Craig, Angus, Skotsko, United Kingdom","Ayr, South Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayr, Ayrshire, Scotland","Ayrshire, Scotland":"Ayrshire, Skotsko, United Kingdom"},"da":{"1174–1249":"1174–1249","1176–1296":"1176–1296","1200–1280":"1200–1280","1